<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('./partials/head') %>
  <title>About — Beelog</title>

  <style>
    .about-container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-title {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-subtitle {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .about-content {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #444;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .about-highlight {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1f73ff;
    }

    .about-footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('./partials/nav') %>

  <div class="about-container">
    <h1 class="about-title">Beelog</h1>
    <p class="about-subtitle">Because ideas deserve a place to live.</p>

    <p class="about-content">
      Beelog is a lightweight blogging platform built for writers, readers,
      and curious minds. It celebrates simplicity — just words, stories, and
      perspectives shared freely without distractions.
    </p>

    <p class="about-content">
      Whether you're here to journal your journey, publish thoughts, teach,
      or simply explore, Beelog gives you the space to <span class="about-highlight">create</span>,
      <span class="about-highlight">share</span>, and
      <span class="about-highlight">connect</span>.
    </p>

    <% if (user) { %>
       <p class="about-content">
         Logged in as <strong><%= user.email %></strong>.
         Your voice matters — make it heard.
       </p>
    <% } else { %>
       <p class="about-content">
         Have something to say? <a href="/signin">Sign in</a> or <a href="/signup">create an account</a> and start writing.
       </p>
    <% } %>

    <div class="about-footer">
      Built with love, caffeine, and curiosity.
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('./partials/scripts') %>
</body>
</html>
